Name: polycystic kidney disease 1
Definition: A autosomal dominant polycystic kidney disease that has_material_basis_in autosomal dominant inheritance of mutation in the PKD1 gene on chromosome 16p13.3.

Name: polycystic kidney disease 2
Definition: A autosomal dominant polycystic kidney disease that has_material_basis_in autosomal dominant inheritance of mutation in the PKD2 gene on chromosome 4q22.1.

Name: polycystic kidney disease 3
Definition: A autosomal dominant polycystic kidney disease that has_material_basis_in autosomal dominant inheritance of mutation in the GANAB gene on chromosome 11q12.3.
